---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<section class='box skills'>
  <div class='stack gap-2 lg:gap-4'>
    <Icon icon='terminalWindow' color='var(--accent-regular)' size='2.5rem' gradient />
    <h2>Full Stack</h2>
    <p>
      Skilled in both frontend and backend, with a primary focus on building secure, efficient, and
      scalable backend systems.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class='stack gap-2 lg:gap-4'>
    <Icon icon='puzzle' color='var(--accent-regular)' size='2.5rem' gradient />
    <h2>Problem Solver</h2>
    <p>
      Detail-oriented and analytical, I tackle challenges with a clear approach, creating efficient
      and reliable solutions.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class='stack gap-2 lg:gap-4'>
    <Icon icon='binoculars' color='var(--accent-regular)' size='2.5rem' gradient />
    <h2>Tech Explorer</h2>
    <p>
      Always on the lookout for new tools and technologies to implement effective and modern
      solutions.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .box {
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background-color: var(--gray-999_40);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .skills {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .skills h2 {
    @apply text-xl-custom;
  }

  .skills p {
    color: var(--gray-400);
  }

  @media (min-width: 50em) {
    .box {
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      padding: 2.5rem;
    }

    .skills {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 5rem;
    }

    .skills h2 {
      @apply text-2xl-custom;
    }
  }
</style>
